<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/19588629" target="_blank" data-id="15427" data-za-element-name="Title">
一名合格的前端工程师的知识结构是怎样的？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/19588629/answer/12447591">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="98187">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="12447591"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>393</a>
</div>

