<div class="feed-main">
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/39835502" target="_blank" data-id="8141576" data-za-element-name="Title">
开发人员可以分为哪几类？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/39835502/answer/83706662">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="28913143">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="83706662"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>383</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">383</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label sr-only">反对</span>
</button>
</div>



<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$yang-fang-zhou-52"
target="_blank" href="/people/yang-fang-zhou-52"
>杨方舟</a></span><span title="前端菜鸡、手办和N比例火车模型爱好者" class="bio">
前端菜鸡、手办和N比例火车模型爱好者
</span>
</span>
</div>

