<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/41170426" target="_blank" data-id="8675532" data-za-element-name="Title">
新手适合学什么计算机语言？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/41170426/answer/90171934">
