>叛逆者</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span></span><span class="badge-summary"><a href="/people/minmin.gong#hilightbadge" target="_blank">计算机图形学、C++话题优秀回答者</a></span>



