<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="3574154" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="haochuan" data-entry-url="/question/28478379/answer/40983886">

<textarea hidden class="content">每天8个必刷的网站...供参考&lt;br&gt;1. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.lynda.com/member.aspx&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Online video tutorials &amp;amp; training&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.coursera.org&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Coursera - Free Online Courses From Top Universities&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//scotch.io&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Scotch ♥ Developers bringing fire to the people.&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//javascriptweekly.com&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;JavaScript Weekly: A Free, Weekly Email Newsletter&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//html5weekly.com&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;HTML5 Weekly: A Free, Weekly Email Newsletter&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;6. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//medium.com&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Medium&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;7. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.smashingmagazine.com&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Smashing Magazine&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;8. &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//css-tricks.com&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;CSS-Tricks&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">

每天8个必刷的网站...供参考 1. <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.lynda.com/member.aspx" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Online video tutorials &amp; training<i class="icon-external"></i></a> 2. <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.coursera.org" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Coursera - Free Online Courses From Top Universities<i class="icon-external"></i></a> 3. <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//scotch.io" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Scotch ♥ Developers bringing fire to the people.<i class="icon-external"></i></a> 4. <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//javascriptweekly.com" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">JavaScript Weekly: A Free, Weekly Email Newsletter<i class="icon-external"></i></a> 5. <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//html5weekly.com" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">HTML5 …<i class="icon-external"></i></a>

<a href="/question/28478379/answer/40983886" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>

</div>



<p class="visible-expanded"><a itemprop="url" class="answer-date-link meta-item" target="_blank" href="/question/28478379/answer/40983886">发布于 2015-03-03</a></p>

