<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/19653241" target="_blank" data-id="41199" data-za-element-name="Title">
使用 Node.js 的优势和劣势都有哪些？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/19653241/answer/14969381">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="1112595">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="14969381"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>373</a>
</div>

